Module kivakit.microservice

Package com.telenav.kivakit.microservice.protocols.rest.openapi

package com.telenav.kivakit.microservice.protocols.rest.openapi
  • Annotation Types Summary
    Annotation Type
    Description
    OpenApiExcludeMember
    Indicates that a supertype (class or interface) member (field or method) should be excluded from the OpenAPI specification for a MicroserviceRestService even if they were included in the supertype with OpenApiExcludeMember.
    OpenApiIncludeMember
    Indicates that a member (method or field) should be included in the OpenAPI specification produced for a MicroserviceRestService
    OpenApiIncludeMemberFromSuperType
    Indicates that a supertype (class or interface) member (method or field) should be included in the OpenAPI specification for a MicroserviceRestService
    OpenApiIncludeType
    Indicates that a type should be included in the OpenAPI specification for a MicroserviceRestService
    OpenApiRequestHandler
    Adds metadata to a MicroservletRequest handler.
